
// This Hyperlambda code uses logical conditions to evaluate if a user's email matches a verified token and if the type is either 'name' or 'email'. The [and] slot ensures both conditions are true, while the nested [or] slot checks if either type condition is met.
and
   user.eq:x:@auth.token.verify/*/email
   or
      type.eq:name
      type.eq:email
